cu.explanation_en: Setting the integrity algorithm to the unknown enum 'nia9' will cause negotiation failure during the security negotiation phase and NAS registration rejection.

du.explanation_en: Setting the maximum MIMO layers to an unsupported value of 5 will cause configuration validation failure and prevent proper radio resource allocation.
du.explanation_zh: 將最大 MIMO 層數設定為不支援的值 5，會導致配置驗證失敗，並阻止適當的無線資源分配。
